## Accepting Bitcoin


A simple guide to accepting bitcoin, an innovative payment network and a new kind of money. 

Bitcoin is the first scarce digital object the world has ever seen, it is scarce like silver and gold, and can be sent over the internet, radio, satellite etc. 

Bitcoin is different than what you know and use every day. Before you start using Bitcoin, there are a few things that you need to know in order to use it securely and avoid common pitfalls. 
